0challenges%20these%20communities%20face.%20By%20focusing%20on%20farming%20and%20building%20local%20resilience%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20connects%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20with%20social%20inequalities%20and%20shows%20why%20solutions%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20local%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dasra%2C%20this%20approach%20is%20not%20new.%20Over%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20the%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%20co-founded%20by%20Neera%20Nundy%20and%20Deval%20Sanghavi%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20more%20than%20%24330%20million%20toward%20social%20causes%2C%20supported%20over%201%2C500%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20positively%20impacted%20approximately%20170%20million%20lives.%20One%20of%20its%20most%20effective%20strategies%20has%20been%20to%20build%20alliances%20with%20like-minded%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%2010to19%20Alliance%2C%20which%20empowers%20adolescents%2C%20especially%20girls%2C%20to%20make%20positive%20life%20choices%2C%20to%20the%20National%20Faecal%20Sludge%20and%20Septage%20Management%20(NFSSM)%20Alliance%2C%20which%20works%20with%20governments%20and%20municipalities%20to%20address%20liquid%20waste%2C%20collaboration%20has%20often%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Dasra%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20rural%20Maharashtra%2C%20Pragati%20Abhiyan%20is%20reviving%20native%20millet%20farming%20to%20fight%20malnutrition%20and%20climate%20stress.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-10_11zon-1755609802-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet