%20directly%20from%20partners%20about%20priorities%20within%20the%20climate%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerged%20from%20these%20conversations%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98ClimateRISE%20Alliance%E2%80%99%20(CRA)%2C%20launched%20in%20early%202023.%20Bringing%20together%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20intermediary%20groups%2C%20and%20funders%2C%20the%20CRA%20aims%20to%20shape%20%E2%80%9Can%20India%20view%E2%80%9D%20on%20intersectional%20climate%20action%2C%20create%20a%20common%20vocabulary%2C%20and%20enable%20multi-stakeholder%20engagement%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities.%20A%20design%20grant%20from%20the%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%20supported%20its%20establishment.%20Today%2C%20about%2070%20organisations%20are%20part%20of%20the%20CRA%2C%20with%20Dasra%20serving%20as%20its%20secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20in%20rural%20communities%20discuss%20local%20climate%20challenges%2C%20a%20key%20step%20in%20building%20resilience%20through%20the%20ClimateRISE%20Alliance.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-11_11zon-1-1755610423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489116%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%2025%20years%2C%20Dasra%20has%20channelled%20%24330M%20into%20social%20causes%2C%20building%20alliances%20like%20ClimateRISE%20for%20larger%20impact.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fvillageneemtone-districtsehore-mp-india-december-20th-2417544213%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20solo%20efforts%20to%20a%20common%20table%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20organisations%20to%20join%20the%20CRA%20was%20%E2%80%98Janaagraha%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20nonprofit%20that%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20working%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20Indian%20cities%20by%20collaborating%20with%20residents%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20urban%20local%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20organisation%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20CRA%20since%20its%20inception%20because%20we%20firmly%20believe%20that%20transforming%20our%20cities%20and%20addressing%20climate%20issues%20cannot%20be%20done%20in%20isolation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prarthana%20Ramesh%2C%20Associate%20Director%20at%20Janaagraha.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CRA%20offers%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20collaborate%20with%20like-minded%20partners.%20It%20brings%20together%20diverse%20stakeholders%2C%20from%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20donors%20to%20innovative%20startups%2C%20to%20collectively%20address%20the%20climate%20crisis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Janaagraha%E2%80%99s%20key%20focus%20areas%20is%20bringing%20climate%20action%20to%20the%20local%20level%20in%20cities%20and%20towns.%20This%20means%20finding%20ways%20to%20make%20it%20part%20of%20everyday%20governance%20and%20tackling%20ongoing%20issues%20like%20flooding%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20poor%20air%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20help%20cities%20take%20charge%20and%20respond%20better%20to%20climate%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prarthana%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20central%20to%20our%20work%20with%20the%20CRA%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20urban%20areas%20the%20tools%20and%20strategies%20they%20need%20to%20act%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20early%20member%20was%20%E2%80%98Saahas%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20nonprofit%20specialising%20in%20solid%20waste%20management.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Saahas%20was%20working%20with%20%3Cem%3Egram%20panchayats%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20municipal%20bodies%20in%20northern%20Karnataka%20to%20strengthen%20local%20waste%20systems.%20While%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%20for%20project%20assistance%2C%20they%20learnt%20about%20the%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Assam%2C%20CRA%20partners%20like%20Janaagraha%20are%20helping%20cities%20tackle%20flooding%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20poor%20air%20quality%20through%20local%20action.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-12_11zon-1755612395-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489130%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20CRA%20partners%20like%20Janaagraha%20are%20helping%20cities%20tackle%20flooding%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20poor%20air%20quality%20through%20local%20action.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fimpact-climate-change-heavy-rain-waterlogging-2182037783%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%20Tripathi%2C%20CEO%20of%20Saahas%2C%20remembers%20the%20turning%20point.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20approached%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%20and%20requested%20their%20support%2C%20we%20learnt%20about%20an%20alliance%20that%20was%20being%20put%20together%20with%20Dasra%20anchoring%20it.%20Despite%20working%20for%20years%20in%20the%20solid%20waste%20management%20sector%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20the%20climate%20space%20is%20much%20broader%20and%20that%20we%20need%20to%20collaborate%20with%20other%20organisations%20working%20on%20different%20climate-related%20issues%20such%20as%20air%20pollution%2C%20liquid%20waste%20management%2C%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20and%20similar%20subjects.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Archana%2C%20joining%20the%20CRA%20was%20about%20more%20than%20just%20networking.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20this%20alliance%20as%20a%20real%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20about%20what%20others%20in%20this%20space%20are%20doing%20and%20to%20help%20build%20a%20coherent%20narrative%20around%20climate.%20While%20you%20have%20the%20Disability%20Network%20Alliance%20(DNA)%20for%20organisations%20working%20on%20disabilities%2C%20there%20was%20no%20dedicated%20platform%20or%20alliance%20working%20on%20climate%20issues.%20Joining%20the%20CRA%20was%20a%20step%20towards%20filling%20that%20gap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20alliance%20works%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20strength%20lies%20in%20its%20ability%20to%20bring%20different%20kinds%20of%20expertise%20to%20one%20table.%20Its%20work%20is%20organised%20into%20multiple%20streams%20%E2%80%94%20strategy%20development%2C%20capacity%20building%2C%20knowledge%20sharing%2C%20and%20collaborative%20advocacy.%20Within%20these%2C%20focus%20groups%20address%20specific%20themes%20such%20as%20gender%2C%20agroecology%20(sustainable%20farming%20that%20works%20with%20local%20ecosystems)%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20conservation%2C%20and%20restoration.%20Many%20of%20these%20areas%20overlap%2C%20making%20the%20alliance%20itself%20a%20climate-focused%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20approach%20is%20collaborative%2C%20not%20about%20one%20organisation%20taking%20a%20grant%20to%20run%20a%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Pranay.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20bring%20together%20stakeholders%20around%20a%20specific%20issue%20or%20idea%2C%20involving%20those%20who%20already%20have%20relevant%20expertise%2C%20ongoing%20projects%2C%20research%2C%20or%20resources.%20This%20pooling%20of%20knowledge%20and%20capacity%20allows%20us%20to%20address%20complex%20climate%20challenges%20in%20a%20coordinated%20and%20integrated%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clear%20example%20of%20this%20approach%20is%20%E2%80%98Doh%20Shaher%2C%20Ek%20Rupayan%E2%80%99%20(DSER%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Ten%20Cities%2C%20One%20Vision%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20convergence%20programme%20led%20by%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Affairs%20(DoHUA)%20to%20promote%20sustainable%20urbanisation%20in%2010%20large%20cities%20and%20towns.%20The%20programme%20covers%20critical%20climate-related%20components%20such%20as%20solid%20waste%20management%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20blue-green%20infrastructure%2C%20urban%20planning%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20them%20together%20instead%20of%20working%20in%20silos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bengaluru-based%20Saahas%20strengthens%20waste%20systems%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Assam%2C%20linking%20waste%20management%20with%20climate%20action.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-13_11zon-1755612578-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBengaluru-based%20Saahas%20strengthens%20waste%20systems%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Assam%2C%20linking%20waste%20management%20with%20climate%20action.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fnew-delhi-indiadec-15-2021-pwd-2106411422%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanaagraha%2C%20as%20an%20anchor%20partner%2C%20has%20been%20conducting%20field%20visits%20in%20Assam%20to%20understand%20the%20geography%20and%20identify%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20partner%20organisations%20involved%20include%20Saahas%2C%20Consortium%20for%20DEWATS%20Dissemination%20(CDD)%20Society%20(decentralised%20wastewater%20treatment)%2C%20Centre%20for%20Water%20and%20Sanitation%20(CWAS)%2C%20Kushaagra%20Innovations%20Foundation%20(waste%20management%20solutions)%2C%20Hasiru%20Dala%20(waste%20management)%2C%20and%20Institute%20for%20Transportation%20and%20Development%20Policy%20(ITDP)%20India%20(public%20transport)%2C%20alongside%20local%20groups%20like%20Purvca%20Foundation%20(urban%20mobility)%20and%20The%20Midway%20Journey%20(decentralised%20waste%20management)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prarthana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20CRA%2C%20working%20with%20local%20organisations%20like%20Purvca%20is%20essential.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20works%20in%20Purvanchal%20may%20not%20be%20suitable%20for%20urban%20Assam%20or%20coastal%20Karnataka%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pranay%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20region%20needs%20solutions%20designed%20for%20its%20own%20conditions%20and%20challenges.%20We%20believe%20climate%20action%20should%20be%20owned%20jointly%20by%20local%20communities%20and%20the%20government%2C%20with%20local%20bodies%2C%20district%20administrations%2C%20and%20grassroots%20organisations%20working%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrarthana%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20role%20as%20Janaagraha%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20anchor%20partners%2C%20is%20to%20onboard%20and%20facilitate%20partners%20across%20these%20components%2C%20but%20not%20in%20a%20siloed%20way.%20The%20CRA%20connects%20us%20with%20the%20best%20minds%20across%20sanitation%2C%20solid%20waste%20management%2C%20blue-green%20infrastructure%2C%20urban%20planning%2C%20mobility%2C%20and%20urban%20transport.%20We%20bring%20these%20experts%20together%20to%20think%20creatively%20and%20reimagine%20what%20urbanisation%20can%20look%20like%20for%20these%20cities%20and%20towns.%20We%20aim%20to%20help%20the%20government%20build%20internal%20capacity%20to%20change%20the%20current%20narrative%2C%20as%20well%20as%20introduce%20elements%20of%20innovation%20into%20their%20planning%20and%20thinking%20processes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20part%20of%20the%20DSER%20project%20is%20developing%20%E2%80%98City%20Action%20Plans%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20short-term%2C%20bottom-up%20vision%20documents%20created%20with%20citizen%20input%2C%20reflecting%20local%20contexts%20and%20aspirations%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20These%20plans%20list%20practical%20projects%20and%20initiatives%2C%20aiming%20to%20be%20living%20documents%20that%20evolve%20with%20the%20cities%20instead%20of%20gathering%20dust%20like%20many%20long-term%20master%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Climate%20resilience%20projects%20also%20build%20women%E2%80%99s%20skills%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20making%20communities%20stronger%20against%20future%20shocks.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-14_11zon-1755612744-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489134%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20CRA%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Doh%20Shaher%2C%20Ek%20Rupayan%E2%80%99%20programme%20in%20Assam%20unites%20citizens%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20NGOs%20to%20plan%20climate-ready%20cities.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fgautam-budh-nagar-uttar-pradesh-indiasep-1998225200%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prepare%20these%20plans%2C%20inputs%20are%20gathered%20directly%20from%20citizens%20through%20field%20visits%20and%20workshops.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20capture%20both%20data%20and%20lived%20experiences%20from%20communities%20in%20vulnerable%20districts%20%E2%80%94%20understanding%20how%20climate%20change%20affects%20them%2C%20and%20how%20they%20are%20responding.%20In%20June%202025%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20Dasra%20and%20Janaagraha%20led%20an%20immersive%20field%20visit%20to%20Tezpur%20and%20hosted%20a%20workshop%20in%20Guwahati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20from%20over%2011%20civil%20society%20organisations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20CRA%20partners%20and%20local%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20joined%20local%20government%20officials%20from%20departments%20handling%20drinking%20water%2C%20sanitation%2C%20blue-green%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20transportation.%20These%20strategic%20discussions%20were%20paired%20with%20on-ground%20visits%2C%20giving%20all%20stakeholders%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20how%20these%20services%20are%20managed%20day%20to%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOpening%20doors%20to%20new%20frontiers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Saahas%2C%20the%20CRA%20opened%20doors%20that%20had%20long%20been%20out%20of%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%20Tripathi%20says%20they%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20the%20Northeast%20but%20struggled%20to%20secure%20funding%20or%20a%20practical%20entry%20point.%20%E2%80%9CAbout%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20started%20work%20in%20Assam%20through%20some%20other%20funding.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20active%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20locations%20in%20the%20state.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20CRA%2C%20we%20can%20scale%20our%20work%20in%20more%20cities%20because%20alliance%20partners%20have%20come%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Saahas%20operates%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Jorhat%20and%20Majuli.%20With%20Janaagraha%20taking%20the%20lead%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20proactive%20in%20its%20support.%20%E2%80%9COn%20our%20own%2C%20we%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20clout%20to%20talk%20to%20state%20authorities%20and%20convince%20them%20to%20back%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Archana%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%20has%20helped%20us%20find%20our%20footing%20in%20Assam.%20Now%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20also%20on%20the%20technical%20committee%20in%20Lakhimpur%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20for%20solid%20waste%20management.%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20CRA%20partners%20work%20in%20urban%20spaces.%20%E2%80%98Farmers%20for%20Forests%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Pune-based%20nonprofit%2C%20focuses%20on%20protecting%20and%20restoring%20forest%20cover%20in%20close%20collaboration%20with%20rural%20communities.%20Co-founder%20Krutika%20Ravishankar%20says%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20challenges%20has%20been%20sustaining%20collaboration%20with%20governments%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20players%20in%20forestry%20and%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-15_11zon-1755612846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Community-led%20efforts%20include%20mangrove%20restoration%20in%20Raigad%20district%20and%20forest%20protection%20in%20Gadchiroli.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-15_11zon-1755612846.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-15_11zon-1755612846-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-15_11zon-1755612846-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-15_11zon-1755612846-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffeatured-img-15_11zon-1755612846-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-489135%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFarmers%20for%20Forests%20works%20with%20communities%20to%20restore%20mangroves%20in%20Raigad%20and%20protect%20forests%20in%20Gadchiroli.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fgroup-teener-village-school-kids-planting-2150933195%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20sort%20of%20collaboration%20with%20the%20government%20really%20enables%20impact%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%20than%20one%20organisation%20can%20do%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20can%20be%20tricky.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20follow-up%2C%20document%20sharing%2C%20and%20legwork%20involved%20before%20you%20bring%20them%20on%20board.%20The%20CRA%20has%20been%20really%20helping%20us%20collaborate%20better%20with%20governments%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%20is%20ensuring%20that%20the%20calls%20with%20them%20get%20done%20regularly%2C%20the%20notes%20(from%20our%20meetings)%20are%20maintained%2C%20or%20documents%20they%20need%20to%20further%20our%20projects%20are%20created.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20work%20more%20effectively%20with%20CRA%20than%20working%20alone%20because%20this%20is%20a%20collaboration%20that%20we%20are%20envisioning%20with%20multiple%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20requests%20can%20also%20stretch%20an%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20capacity.%20Krutika%20recalls%20how%20different%20departments%20have%20asked%20them%20for%20everything%20from%20carbon%20finance%20consultancy%20to%20tracking%20elephants%2C%20setting%20up%20and%20running%20mobile%20science%20laboratories%2C%20developing%20climate-relevant%20curricula%2C%20or%20supplying%20two%20lakh%20saplings%20for%20plantation%20drives.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CRA%20knows%20exactly%20which%20partner%20to%20approach%20for%20each%20request%2C%20so%20we%20can%20focus%20on%20our%20core%20expertise%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20from%20restoring%20mangroves%20in%20Raigad%20district%20to%20preventing%20deforestation%20in%20Gadchiroli%20district%20%E2%80%94%20often%20involve%20coordination%20with%20other%20CRA%20partners%20like%20Reap%20Benefit%2C%20Technology%20for%20Wildlife%2C%20Grasslands%20Trust%2C%20and%20EarthFokus%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECrafting%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20story%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20nonprofits%2C%20the%20day-to-day%20demands%20of%20their%20work%20leave%20little%20time%20to%20build%20large%2C%20multi-stakeholder%20collaborations.%20%E2%80%9CGenuine%20collaboration%20is%20often%20difficult%20because%20dedicated%20resources%20like%20funding%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20time%20are%20rarely%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prarthana%20Ramesh%20of%20Janaagraha.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEfforts%20like%20outreach%2C%20bringing%20diverse%20stakeholders%20together%2C%20ensuring%20everyone%20is%20aligned%2C%20and%20having%20a%20catalyst%20or%20facilitator%20to%20drive%20the%20project%20forward%20are%20incredibly%20challenging.%20The%20CRA%20has%20effectively%20filled%20this%20gap%20for%20many%20nonprofits%20like%20us.%20It%20has%20enabled%20us%20to%20build%20partnerships%2C%20collaborations%2C%20and%20coalitions%20more%20easily%2C%20without%20constantly%20worrying%20about%20losing%20focus%20or%20struggling%20to%20secure%20funding.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20co