%80%99s%20heart%20transplant%2C%20which%20held%20up%20a%20mirror%20to%20the%20flaws%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20transplant%20framework.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20struggled%20with%20finding%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20support%20and%20information.%20Despite%20being%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20healthcare%20company%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20still%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20right%20information.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20today.%20ORGAN%20India%20wants%20to%20ensure%20no%20one%20grapples%20with%20the%20same%20doubts.%20ORGAN%20India%20has%20multiple%20ways%20of%20working%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20increases%20the%20number%20of%20donor%20pledges%20in%20India%20through%20large-scale%20information%20dissemination%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351914%2Forgan-donation-in-india-donor-mohan-foundation-dr-sunil-shroff-kbc-episode-kidney-transplant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelps%20anyone%20seeking%20transplants%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20offering%20information%2C%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20also%20offers%20counselling%20services%20and%20monetary%20help%20where%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20spirit%20that%20fuels%20Team%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20ORGAN%20India%2C%20Anika%20is%20looking%20to%20help%20more%20Varuns%20access%20the%20right%20treatment%20modalities%2C%20offering%20them%20a%20lifeline%20of%20hope.%20She%20recalls%20her%20astonishment%20at%20seeing%20Varun%E2%80%99s%20potential%20for%20the%20first%20time%20during%20their%20meeting%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%202023.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20youngest%20among%20the%2032-member%20Team%20India%20contingent%20but%20was%20leading%20it%20with%20his%20energy.%E2%80%9D%20Being%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20transplant%20recipients%20participate%20in%20sports%20at%20a%20global%20stage%20makes%20Anika%20happy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20met%20so%20many%20parents%20who%E2%80%99ve%20donated%20their%20organs%20to%20their%20children%3B%20I%E2%80%99ve%20met%20so%20many%20children%20who%E2%80%99ve%20had%20transplants.%20In%20the%20team%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20had%20siblings%20who%20have%20donated%20organs%20to%20each%20other%3B%20the%20generosity%20of%20spirit%20is%20just%20incredible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20underscores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-3-1755520611.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ORGAN%20India%20is%20the%20official%20manager%20of%20Team%20India%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%20and%20works%20closely%20with%20the%20sportspersons%20in%20the%20build%20up%20to%20the%20event%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-3-1755520611.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-3-1755520611-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-3-1755520611-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-3-1755520611-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-3-1755520611-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488538%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EORGAN%20India%20is%20the%20official%20manager%20of%20Team%20India%20at%20the%20World%20Transplant%20Games%20and%20works%20closely%20with%20the%20sportspersons%20in%20the%20build%20up%20to%20the%20event%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnika%20is%20a%20firm%20believer%20in%20the%20power%20of%20transplants%2C%20a%20message%20that%E2%80%99s%20constantly%20underlined%20by%20ORGAN%20India.%20Seconding%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310277%2Fabhinav-pangtey-shares-myths-about-organ-donation-india-world-transplant-games%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20success%20of%20transplants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20kidney%20transplants%20in%20children%2C%20Dr%20Saumil%20says%2C%20there%20are%20two%20criteria%20of%20success.%20%E2%80%9COne%20is%20the%20success%20of%20the%20graft%20%E2%80%94%20the%20transplanted%20kidney%3B%20the%20second%20is%20the%20success%20in%20the%20survival.%E2%80%9D%20This%20implies%20how%20the%20person%20is%20doing%20after%20the%20transplant.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20our%20centre%2C%20the%20success%20of%20the%20graft%20is%20almost%2095%20percent%20after%20five%20years.%20The%20success%20of%20the%20person%20doing%20well%20is%2099%20to%20100%20percent.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Varun%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point%20of%20a%20successful%20transplant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98My%20mom%20has%20given%20me%20life%20twice%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Deepa%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20transplant%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20Varun%20to%20do%20more%20compared%20to%20what%20he%20could%20earlier.%E2%80%9D%20Calling%20him%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfighter%E2%80%9D%2C%20Dr%20Saumil%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20boy%20who%E2%80%99d%20been%20bunking%20PE%20(physical%20education)%20class%20in%20school%20now%20practises%20for%20hours%20in%20the%20hot%20summer%20sun.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20resolve%20was%20tested%20during%20his%20training%20period%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20games%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20train%20for%20three%20hours%20on%20weekdays%2C%20seven%20hours%20on%20weekends%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20day%20during%20the%20summer%20holidays.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medal%20%E2%80%94%20much%20less%20upending%20expectations%20by%20winning%20three%20%E2%80%94%20was%20never%20on%20the%20cards.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20always%20told%20me%20to%20go%20have%20fun%20at%20the%20games%3B%20%E2%80%98try%20winning%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20said%2C%20but%20I%20remember%20when%20I%20held%20the%20first%20gold%20medal%2C%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20what%20I%E2%80%99d%20actually%20managed.%20My%20mother%20was%20crying%3B%20her%20kidney%2C%20after%20all%2C%20had%20helped%20me%20do%20something%20significant%20for%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varun%20shares.%20Varun%20is%20set%20to%20participate%20once%20again%20in%20the%20ongoing%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Varun%20and%20his%20mother%20Deepa%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20kidney%20donor%20for%20Varun's%20transplant%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fpartition-of-1947-1-1755520390-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5