%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20compliments%20and%20appreciation%20that%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20I%20am%20doing%20very%20well.%20But%20if%20I%20had%20not%20been%20cultivating%20these%20flowers%2C%20not%20only%20would%20I%20be%20losing%20money%20but%20I%20would%20also%20be%20losing%20my%20medium%20of%20releasing%20stress%20because%20these%20plants%20are%20like%20my%20happy%20pills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Parvathy%20Mohanan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755433800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fportulaca-1-1722572713.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D486424%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20weekends%2C%20a%20software%20tester%20from%20Kochi%20nurtures%20300%20vibrant%20Portulaca%20varieties%20from%20half%20an%20acre%E2%80%94fulfilling%2050%E2%80%93100%20orders%20daily%20by%20transforming%20her%20passion%20into%20profit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F486424%2Fkerala-engineer-portulaca-business-1-lakh-month%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Grand%20Jury%20Announced!%20Meet%20the%2010%20Icons%20Choosing%20India%E2%80%99s%20Biggest%20Changemakers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20sees%20a%20problem%20and%20decides%20to%20fix%20it%20%E2%80%94%20not%20for%20fame%2C%20but%20because%20it%20simply%20must%20be%20done%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20change%20India%20needs.%20This%20September%2C%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%3Cstrong%3EOptum%20Presents%20The%20Better%20India%20Showcase%202025%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20M3M%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20will%20honour%20the%20people%20who%20build%20those%20changes.%20It%20spotlights%20everyday%20courage%2C%20compassion%20in%20action%2C%20and%20solutions%20born%20of%20lo